  "title": "Preschool Cook Cum Cleaner",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a cook cum cleaner for a preschool near Beauty World MRT.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u>Responsibilities:</u></p>\n<p>- Prepare breakfast, lunch and teabreak for children according to the menu provided</p>\n<p>- Prepare lunch for staff</p>\n<p>- Help in serving children during mealtimes</p>\n<p>- Help to make milk for children</p>\n<p>- Collect back the dirty bowls after meals and wash the bowls, plates, cups and utensils</p>\n<p>- Maintain cleanliness of kitchen</p>\n<p>- Keep stock of ingredients in kitchen and prepare grocery list every week</p>\n<p>- Do grocery shopping as and when needed</p>\n<p>- Prepare special food items during festivals/centre events</p>\n<p>- Clean and upkeep cleanliness and hygiene of centre</p>\n<p>- Sweep and mop the floor, wipe furniture, wash toilets etc.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u>Requirements:</u></p>\n<p>- Possess a food and safety hygiene cert</p>\n<p>- Has good kitchen hygiene</p>\n<p>- Enjoy working in an environment with children</p>\n<p>- Proactive and takes instructions well</p>\n<p>Hours: 44h/week 7am-4.30pm</p>\n<p>Location: Beauty World</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Kindly contact us at 8090 1816 and we will get in touch with you as soon as possible.</p>",
